# Useless Facts App - Project Structure

## Project Overview

Next.js 13 app with AI-powered fact generation, topic extraction (NER/TF-IDF), and admin interface. Built with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, and Turso database.

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: Next.js 13 (App Router), React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- **Backend**: Next.js API Routes, Turso (libSQL) database
- **AI/ML**: Google Gemini 2.0 Flash Lite for NER, OpenAI embeddings
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with custom CSS variables, shadcn/ui components
- **Validation**: Zod schemas for type-safe data validation
- **Deployment**: Vercel with automatic CI/CD

## File Organization

- **Components**: [components/](mdc:components/) - UI components
  - [components/ui/](mdc:components/ui/) - shadcn/ui base components
- **API Routes**: [app/api/](mdc:app/api/) - Next.js 13 App Router API routes
- **Library**: [lib/](mdc:lib/) - utilities, database functions, validation
- **Types**: [types/](mdc:types/) - TypeScript type definitions
- **Configuration**: [config/](mdc:config/) - site configuration
- **Styles**: [styles/](mdc:styles/) - global Tailwind CSS

## Key Files

- Main database client: [lib/db.ts](mdc:lib/db.ts)
- Database schema: [lib/schema.ts](mdc:lib/schema.ts)
- Validation schemas: [lib/validation.ts](mdc:lib/validation.ts)
- Utility functions: [lib/utils.ts](mdc:lib/utils.ts)
- Database initialization: [lib/init-db.ts](mdc:lib/init-db.ts)

## Environment Variables

- `TURSO_DATABASE_URL`: Database connection string
- `TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN`: Database authentication token
- `GOOGLE_API_KEY`: Google Gemini API key
- `CRON_SECRET`: Secret for cron job authentication
